      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">14.408-2</ph> Responsible bidder-reasonableness of price.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d846e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d873e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            The contracting officer shall determine that a prospective contractor is responsible (see <xref href="Subpart_9.1.dita#FAR_Subpart_9_1"
                        base="i1116049"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpartÂ  9.1</xref>) and that the prices offered are reasonable before awarding the contract. The price analysis techniques in <xref href="15.404-1.dita#FAR_15_404_1"
                        base="i1106135"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">15.404-1</xref>(b) may be used as guidelines. In each case the determination shall be made in the light of all prevailing circumstances. Particular care must be taken in cases where only a single bid is received.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d873e21">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            The price analysis shall consider whether bids are materially unbalanced (see <xref href="15.404-1.dita#FAR_15_404_1"
                        base="i1106135"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">15.404-1</xref>(g)).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
